@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_wqnppe(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos((v2 / wp.exp(v1 + 0.90)))
    v0 = ((wp.exp(v2 + 0.75) / (v0 + 0.10 / v1 + 0.77)) - v2)
    v1 = wp.cos(0.68)
    data[tid] = v0
